    {
      "id": "insight:ff7658e130fae613",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Private credit's current prominence is often discussed with polarized viewpoints, ranging from minor market fluctuations to predictions of a major financial crisis.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "opinion",
        "position_hint": 0.02
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:7c68521edec916da",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "point zero, right, and it's very difficult to find nuanced",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 1546,
        "char_end": 1604,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 88840,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 92399,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:0da22387183b9d9a",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "We keep getting these headlines over the last several weeks,",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 441,
        "char_end": 501,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 35479,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 38919,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:97f259ce44a7b7ca",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The historical evolution of the bond market, from investment grade and high-yield to leveraged loans, created the conditions for private credit's emergence.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.14
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:d83ff75c1c6f11ff",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "highly levered companies companies that didn't have investment grade balance",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 7808,
        "char_end": 7884,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 420839,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 425640,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:2007e1df3b8cde08",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "That evolved into the leverage loan market.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 8235,
        "char_end": 8278,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 445000,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 448120,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:e214479f81201777",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Post-2008 financial crisis regulations on banks, specifically concerning leverage limits, created a lending vacuum that private credit filled.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.16
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:424d546053ee8125",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "There is an explicit prevention from banks lending to companies",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 8918,
        "char_end": 8981,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 485280,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 488640,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:409ba3f83b19455d",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "for lending outside of the bank market.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 9063,
        "char_end": 9102,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 493160,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 497320,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:3cb5613f06913ea2",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "both corporated and individuals, so you saw pretty strict capital requirements.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 8828,
        "char_end": 8907,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 479080,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 484960,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:88ad7e7d59cb7a73",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "GE Capital's historical financing of diverse assets like aircraft and healthcare equipment represents an early, significant form of private credit.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.18
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:a9585cee92283c50",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "credit under the GE umbrella for many, many, many years.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 10160,
        "char_end": 10216,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 551720,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 555040,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:d5cad612a66ad301",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "financing railcars, they were financing aircraft engines, they were financing",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 10299,
        "char_end": 10376,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 558120,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 562720,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:2c9551d2f0fcf44c",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The growth of private credit is driven by both investor demand for higher yields and borrowers' restricted access to traditional bank lending.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.3
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:51a706b3e49db158",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "together at the same time and really fueled the growth",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 17118,
        "char_end": 17172,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 929800,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 932600,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:6908ba93957a2cdb",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "they needed to find alternatives to fund their businesses and",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 16985,
        "char_end": 17046,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 922800,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 926240,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:532117abec9078fc",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "and better performing assets than they had in the early",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 16587,
        "char_end": 16642,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 901160,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 903800,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:e9e263873facb2e1",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The private credit market has become highly competitive, potentially leading to less favorable terms for lenders, such as reduced interest rates and weaker covenants.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "claim",
        "position_hint": 0.41
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:85d2b617b8c931a0",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "the investment opportunity and then they go call the funds.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 22831,
        "char_end": 22890,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1222440,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1225520,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:5950c8c1d36e5716",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "find investments, which creates this competitive environment that you alluded",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 23121,
        "char_end": 23198,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1235359,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1239640,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:19a4e21fca4aba8f",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "in the credit world is either lower interest rate, weaker covenance,",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 23514,
        "char_end": 23582,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1253359,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1258000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:cc63bba3dc37efe7",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Institutional private credit funds typically operate on a draw-down basis, matching LP commitments with sourced assets over a defined term.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.42
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:2c22afb6a8b862d1",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "those institutional funds are generally DRAWDOUN funds, so they're allowed",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 24102,
        "char_end": 24176,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1282560,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1286639,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:c21ad1f569f3dfc8",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Private credit funds targeting retail investors may offer liquidity concessions, creating pressure to invest capital rapidly.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.44
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:fb0c253fabb19840",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "concessions on the liquidity right, because it makes it easier",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 25109,
        "char_end": 25171,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1336400,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1339800,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:707c7b8fe1b10a2b",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "to raise money really fast.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 25377,
        "char_end": 25404,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1350080,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1352920,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:d469b4ea1d17cff8",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "because they've just said, Okay, we can raise a lot",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 25439,
        "char_end": 25490,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1353320,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1355320,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:6b1efc25178caedf",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Rapid deployment of capital in private credit funds can lead to a degradation of credit underwriting standards.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "claim",
        "position_hint": 0.46
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:987efcbc9ee8082a",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "is too strong work, but really more bad underwriting, weaker underwriting,",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 27669,
        "char_end": 27743,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1460680,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1465240,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:6841b7eec1a52349",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "because they've just said, Okay, we can raise a lot",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 25439,
        "char_end": 25490,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1353320,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1355320,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:b6bd988a0ccfc1cc",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "of credit underwriting because if you don't invest those dollars quickly,",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 25824,
        "char_end": 25897,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1370440,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1374640,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:d9ed08ad28eab748",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The Osterweis Strategic Income Fund operates with an unconstrained mandate, allowing flexibility across the fixed income spectrum.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.1
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:b7983f11c0b774d8",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "only fixed income fund that our private clients needed.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 5399,
        "char_end": 5454,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 284159,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 287400,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:3000b565f55075ed",
