        "char_start": 5468,
        "char_end": 5503,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 287800,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 290400,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:ff3ab6d88a1a3833",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "risky ways to play those most attractive parts at any",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 5860,
        "char_end": 5913,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 311560,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 315159,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:f26e738c4229fa13",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Insurance companies are natural investors in private credit due to their long-duration liabilities and ability to harvest illiquidity premiums.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.38
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:6333de0e68e77b7a",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "assets and there's generally not a rush for those assets.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 21731,
        "char_end": 21788,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1164880,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1168440,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:b6c2741c402df963",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "insurance companies have long been investors in private assets, and",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 21205,
        "char_end": 21272,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1139119,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1142280,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0005 - What_s Actually Going On With Private Credit_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:fb9f5ef9145a2b18",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The sourcing of private credit deals requires a proactive, door-knocking approach, differing from the more passive deal-finding methods in other markets.",
        "episode_id": "74a9745d-6825-4bfc-abc3-b43601639f72",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.39
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:595504eb7d48c3a9",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
